3 December 2015Deputy Minister of Communications Stella Ndabeni-Abrahams will give a message of support to the National Prosecution Authority- led Imbizo and later host the Christmas party for the elderly in Diepsloot as she continues with the second part of the Imbizo.The Deputy Minister of Communications Stella Ndabeni Abrahams will collaborate with National Prosecution Authority to roll out the Imbizo Focus Week programme on Friday 4th December 2015 in Diepsloot, JHB, Gauteng.Members of the media are invited as follows:Date: Friday, 4h December 2015 Time: 09h00 Venue: Skills Development Centre, DiepslootRSVPs: Senzi Ngubane Cell: 060 647 6705 Email: senzeni@doc.gov.zaEnquiries:Mzimasi Ngqelu Cell: 0769043557 Email: mzi@doc.gov.zaIssued by Ministry of Communications